                                   ConformerAtom[] ref,
                                   double ang,
                                   List atoms)
This methodName will rotate the coordinates of 'atoms' such that tor == ang - atoms in 'tor' should be ordered such that the 3rd atom is the pivot around which atoms rotate ang is in degrees.
